reviewText: Part of this Special Editon is the main characters hiding from a clown terminator, another part is the main characters on a treasure hunt and the special edition is the main characters in a Frantenstien spoof.

This movie was great, The TV show was hilarious, and the fact that this and many other great shows have been canceled and the crap thats on tv instead keeps getting renewed makes me feel that people like me aren't watching enough tv to save the good stuff and teenage girls are watching way too much tv
